description:
Cassandra Nix is a college freshman excited to go to her first frat party. There she is hoping to hook up with her crush Danny, but he has different ideas. He lures the excited girl into his room then handcuffs her to the bed and once she is bound and helpless opens the door for all his frat friends to take turns on her holes.
This is Cassandra Nix's FIRST GANGBANG EVER!!!!
Directed by James Deen
title: The Frat Party: Starring Cassandra Nix in her FIRST GANGBANG! 12 guys
